# Data Folder

This folder is reserved for dataset references and sample inputs.

The full datasets used in this project are not included in the public repository due to:
- file size constraints
- licensing and source restrictions
- repository cleanliness

Datasets used in this project:
- BBC News
- Reuters-21578
- AG News
- Scraped articles from CNN, The Guardian, and TechCrunch

The notebooks assume that the cleaned input files are available locally before execution.
